Add a shared `extractApprovalData()` function to `packages/relay/src/lib/payload-utils.ts`. This function extracts tool approval data from an unknown relay envelope payload, following the exact pattern of existing helpers like `extractTextDelta()` and `extractErrorMessage()` in the same file.

**Interface definition** (add to `payload-utils.ts`):

